      "role": "user",
      "content": "memories don't change the fact that the house is empty. it feels pointless. like i'm just performing these little rituals for no one. wake up, make coffee for one, sit in the silence, go to sleep. it's not just sadness anymore... it's just a total absence of meaning. i don't see the point in the routine anymore.",
